The Great Red Dragon

As time went by, we noticed the great wonders of the old world. We are careful to believe in the great absurd tales of the ancient beasts, with a little notion of their true form, sculpting our heroes and gods along the way, centuries past emerging with uncanny other. Only to find out that the true form of immortal is being made after the disappearance into the void, sands of time.
